
/*
 * This Hyperlambda code snippet adds nodes retrieved from the [.arguments] node to the [where] clause of a [data.read] operation. The [add] slot is used to insert these nodes, which are fetched using the [get-nodes] slot, into the specified location within the current node structure. 
 * 
 * 1. [add] - Inserts nodes into the specified location within the node structure.
 * 2. [get-nodes] - Retrieves nodes from the [.arguments] node to be added.
 */
add:x:./*/data.read/*/where/*
   get-nodes:x:@.arguments/*
